text: Joe Jefferson Clubhouse is located in Saddle River, Bergen County, New Jersey, United States. The building was built in 1925 and was added to the National Register of Historic Places on August 29, 1986. ==See also== *National Register of Historic Places listings in Bergen County, New Jersey ==External links== * Google Street View of Joe Jefferson Clubhouse ==References== Category:Buildings and structures completed in 1925 Category:Buildings and structures in Bergen County, New Jersey Category:Clubhouses on the National Register of Historic Places in New Jersey Category:National Register of Historic Places in Bergen County, New Jersey Category:Saddle River, New Jersey Category:New Jersey Register of Historic Places
title: Joe Jefferson Clubhouse
